text: The 1990 555 Asian Open was a professional ranking snooker tournament that took place between 29 October and 3 November 1990 at the Guangdong TV studios in Guangzhou, China. Defending champion Stephen Hendry won the tournament by defeating Dennis Taylor 9–3 in the final. __TOC__ ==Main draw== ==References== Category:1990 in snooker Category:Snooker in China
